2	       wang	            3	            2	        1573725836189_Wang Ft Sonam Bajwa - Ammy Virk(DJJOhAL.Com).mp3	
4	       Teri Khaamiyan	    5	            1	        1573726306407_Teri Khaamiyan - Akhil(DJJOhAL.Com).mp3	
